The paper presents a modeling language for architecture and behavior modeling of Cyber-Physical Systems, which falls under the software engineering (cs.SE) and systems and control (cs.SY) sub-categories. The language is implemented using the MontiCore DSL framework, which is related to programming languages (cs.PL). The paper also discusses well-formedness rules and semantics, which are related to logic (cs.LO) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
